HEADWORD: Committer
<hw>Com*mit"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who commits; one who does or perpetrates.</def>
<rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A fornicator.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>T.
Decker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Committible</ent>⟦br⟧
